<title>Driving boats of migrants</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Over a thousand people &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/jun/29/europe-war-people-smugglers-italy&#34;&gt;face imprisonment in Italy&lt;/a&gt; for driving boats full of migrants â€” because they were told to drive or be shot. But this is just the clearest of the stupidities in the European campaign to arrest smugglers.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
