<published>2018-06-10T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-06-10T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Copyright censorship filters</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The EU governments joined the EU executive in supporting  &lt;a href=&#34;https://cdt.org/blog/copyright-eu-parliament-must-step-up-council-adopts-ill-advised-position/&#34;&gt;mandatory copyright censorship filters&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This is terribly dangerous.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CFKFW400W4KCC5N5025ZGH7W.html"/>
</entry>
