<title>TSA&#39;s harass-list</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The TSA&#39;s harass-list for travelers that have protested or complained &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.latimes.com/opinion/op-ed/la-oe-bovard-tsa-watchlist-20180528-story.html&#34;&gt;violates civil liberties&lt;/a&gt;, especially given that the agency tends to cover up and demand immunity for when it attacks people.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CFKFW400VGGR5HY2W6M8EAPF.html"/>
