<title>Commitment to democracy</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &amp;quot;The research suggests that when intolerant white people fear democracy may benefit marginalized people, they  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nbcnews.com/think/opinion/trump-effect-new-study-connects-white-american-intolerance-support-authoritarianism-ncna877886&#34;&gt;abandon their commitment to democracy&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;quot;   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CFKFW400T74M0WHP4TKYZ8KF.html"/>
