<published>2018-06-10T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-06-10T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>&#34;Alternative&#34; cancer treatments</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Some common &amp;quot;alternative&amp;quot; cancer treatments are  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/science/2014/dec/03/alternative-therapies-risk-effectiveness-of-cancer-treatment-researchers-find&#34;&gt;worse than useless&lt;/a&gt; â€” they undermine the effectiveness of drugs and radiation.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CFKFW400QBTQMFKVSN71XAVE.html"/>
</entry>
